{
  "stem": "19441.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the same was the SS woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was [? the ?] thousand German woman for the start and a thousand SS woman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they somehow couldn't count us together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not only our barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was more coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we had to stand for hours 'til they counted us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Cold.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that first day, they put us back, because they didn't have the program for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the next day, they was looking for people to work inside, in the kitchen, in the [INAUDIBLE], in the so-called hospital, in the-- where they sew, sew room.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so that was, because they had to establish-- we started a new camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why they-- they had to establish it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't go nowhere, because I was occupied with four girls who lost their mind for a while.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I was trying to bring them back to the consciousness that they are not crazy, just a shock what-- what happened.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They couldn't believe that it's possible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg pardon?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did remember one, but I've forgotten, so it would take me long to bring her back to memory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was very surprised at how good they are now after few days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they carried me around and they said, we want Magda, we want Magda, because they were so grateful, because they knew if somebody will found out that they are crazy, then the-- straight away the news went on that they got a phenol injection to the heart and they would be dead in a minute.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So now when they found out that I saved their lives, so they were very grateful.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then it happened that the woman in our room-- which was over 600.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a big room.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
